text: Had the best first tennis lesson ever with Desmond! Very patient and gave great insights in learning the fundamentals. Very fun and highly recommend!

Desmond is a fantastic tennis coach!
I’ve had the pleasure of taking lessons with him, and I highly recommend him for both beginners and intermediate players. He has a great teaching style – patient, encouraging, and knows exactly how to break down techniques so they’re easy to understand.

Desmond makes learning tennis fun while still challenging you to improve with every session. His tips on form, footwork, and strategy have helped me build confidence on the court. Whether you're just starting or looking to level up your skills, Desmond is the coach you need!

As beginners, my friend and I had an amazing experience in our tennis lessons with Desmond. Even though our balls went flying all over the court, he was always patient and encouraging. The atmosphere in class was relaxed and enjoyable.
Great lesson for my son and myself. Very clear explanation from Coach Desmond. I find I have improved my swing a lot in just one lesson!
Desmond is an awesome teacher! Highly personable, knowledgeable and great to learn from! Would recommend
